name: Jello Jump
description:
WASD to move , mouse 1 to dive , space to jump and space for jet-pack

Play as tiny Blobo where your goal is to collect the stars and make your way to the top bouncing on jellos! Green jellos help Blobo by filling up his jello meter/health, make sure not to hit too many red jellos!As they deplete your jello meter/health.

Game Developed in 2 weeks by a group of FIEA students

Nassir, Dylan, Kyle, Alexis & Gregory
